<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Dependency-Updates on Sujith Quintelier</title><link>https://quintelier.dev/update_tags/dependency-updates/</link><description>Recent content in Dependency-Updates on Sujith Quintelier</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 00:24:41 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://quintelier.dev/update_tags/dependency-updates/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>github: Dependabot version updates now support the Deno ecosystem</title><link>https://quintelier.dev/updates/dependabot-version-updates-now-support-the-deno-ecosystem/</link><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 00:24:41 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://quintelier.dev/updates/dependabot-version-updates-now-support-the-deno-ecosystem/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Dependabot version updates now support Deno. The support is for version updates only, not security updates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Source:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href="https://github.blog/changelog/2026-06-09-dependabot-version-updates-now-support-the-deno-ecosystem" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>github: Dependabot version updates now support the sbt ecosystem</title><link>https://quintelier.dev/updates/dependabot-version-updates-now-support-the-sbt-ecosystem/</link><pubDate>Tue, 26 May 2026 16:10:46 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://quintelier.dev/updates/dependabot-version-updates-now-support-the-sbt-ecosystem/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Dependabot version updates now support the sbt ecosystem. You can add &lt;code&gt;sbt&lt;/code&gt; to &lt;code&gt;dependabot.yml&lt;/code&gt;, and Dependabot will monitor &lt;code&gt;build.sbt&lt;/code&gt; inputs and open pull requests when newer commits are available.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Source:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href="https://github.blog/changelog/2026-05-26-dependabot-version-updates-now-support-the-sbt-ecosystem" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>